propmt-llm.md

# Local .terraform directories (Plugins and modules)
**/.terraform/*

# .tfstate files (Contains sensitive data and secrets)
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*

# Crash log files
crash.log
crash.*

# Variables files (Where you might put secrets/sensitive values)
*.tfvars
*.tfvars.json

# Override files
override.tf
override.tf.json
_override.tf
_override.tf.json

# Ignore CLI configuration files
.terraformrc
terraform.rc

# Ignore GCP Service Account Keys (Safety first!)
*.json